# Commands

- Lint: `make backend-lint`
- Test: `make backend-test`
- Build static: `make backend-build-static` (after UI changes)
- Migrate: `make migrate` or `make dev-migrate`
- Dev server: `make dev-backend` (Daphne ASGI for WebSocket)
- Dev all: `make dev-login-ready-services`

# Verification Checklist

Before completing any task:
- [ ] `make backend-lint` passes
- [ ] `make backend-test` passes
- [ ] Tenant scoping verified (no cross-customer data leaks)
- [ ] Type hints added to new functions
- [ ] Static assets rebuilt if UI changes (`make backend-build-static`)
- [ ] Migrations created/applied if model changes
- [ ] React islands registered in `islands.tsx` if new component added
